snippet.textDisplay:
I thought up a helluva boss and hazbin hotel crossover:
We find out who killed vaggie and alastor calls the immediate murder professionals without telling vaggie or angel dust. When they come, angel is buying drugs and he falls into the portal to the human world. Instead of going back into hell he stays and after a while he starts to look more human. While The IMP are looking for the suspect, angel dust sees them and says “Hey! Your the guys from that sh**ty tv advert!”
When the IMP see angel they notice how human he looks and tell him to go back into the portal. Angel dust refuses. When the IMP go out the portal, they go to hazbin hotel to tell them what happened. Alastor goes in but he got lost and couldn’t find angel so he looks more human too.
Vaggie already knows what happens in when you stay on earth too long so she doesn’t go in. Since Charlie was born in hell, she wouldn’t turn back to a human. She goes into the portal to see angel dust skinny dipping in a pool and alastor chasing a deer with a knife. They all look like humans. Charlie grabs a towel and throws it to angel before dragging him into the portal. It then shows it in hazbin hotel with Luna screaming “GET SOME F**KING CLOTHES ON” at angel, whose four arms are already back. When Charlie goes to alastor, he has killed the deer. “Well hello, Charlie, your looking nice today” comments alastor (but this time his voice doesn’t sound like it’s on the radio). Charlie tells alastor to drop the deer and go into the portal, but alastor doesn’t listen and goes into the portal with the deer, which, when their in hell, turns into a demon with knifes as it’s antlers. Moxxie pulls a confused face. “well, here’s what you wanted”said blitzo, handing vaggie the bag with the body of who killed her.
roll credits

P.S. if you actually do this please credit me
